### ========================================
### TOPIC HIERARCHY - Recursive Tree Tests
### ========================================

### Create root topic - Programming
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Programming",
  "content": "General programming concepts and languages"
}

### Create JavaScript topic (child of Programming)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript",
  "content": "JavaScript programming language",
  "parentTopicId": "{PROGRAMMING_TOPIC_ID}"
}

### Create Variables topic (child of JavaScript)  
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Variables",
  "content": "JavaScript variables and data types",
  "parentTopicId": "{JAVASCRIPT_TOPIC_ID}"
}

### Create Functions topic (child of JavaScript)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Functions", 
  "content": "JavaScript functions and scope",
  "parentTopicId": "{JAVASCRIPT_TOPIC_ID}"
}

### Create Arrow Functions topic (child of Functions)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arrow Functions",
  "content": "ES6 arrow functions syntax and usage", 
  "parentTopicId": "{FUNCTIONS_TOPIC_ID}"
}

### Get complete topic tree starting from Programming
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{PROGRAMMING_TOPIC_ID}/tree

### Get subtree starting from JavaScript
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{JAVASCRIPT_TOPIC_ID}/tree

### Get leaf topic tree (should have empty children)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/{VARIABLES_TOPIC_ID}/tree

### Test with non-existent topic
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/non-existent-id/tree